  "notes": [
    "This case report describes two different mechanisms for junctional rhythm: preoperative rhythm due to primary pacemaker slowing, and intraoperative rhythm due to adrenaline-induced sympathetic stimulation",
    "The temporal relationship between local anesthesia administration and junctional rhythm onset (15 minutes) suggests a causal relationship"
